@startuml UC-11
' SnowReach - Use Case Diagrams - Group C: Work Execution and Completion
' UC-11, UC-12, UC-13, UC-14

skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #f5f5f5
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #555555
skinparam ActivityDiamondBackgroundColor #fff3cd
skinparam ActivityDiamondBorderColor #856404
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #e8f4f8
skinparam NoteBorderColor #2980b9
skinparam ArrowColor #333333

title UC-11 - Begin Work (Mark In Progress)

start

:Precondition: Job is in Confirmed state.;

:Worker opens active job and taps "Start Job";

if (Requester cancels before Worker starts?) then (yes)
  :Job -> Cancelled\n$10 fee deducted from escrow (Phase 2)\nWorker -> Available;
  stop
else (no)
endif

:Liability acknowledgement screen shown\n"By proceeding, you confirm full personal\nresponsibility and liability for all work\nat this property, including actions of any\nperson assisting or working on your behalf."\nCheckbox cannot be pre-selected.;

if (Dispatcher or crew will perform work?) then (yes)
  :Worker checks secondary checkbox:\n"Someone other than me will perform this work";
  :Worker enters on-site person's full name(s);
  :Requester immediately notified of who will be on-site;
  :15-minute Accept/Decline window opens for Requester;
  if (Requester taps Decline?) then (yes)
    :Job reverts to Confirmed\n(NOT Cancelled - no cancellation fee applies)\nWorker can correct disclosure\nor submit Cannot Complete;
    stop
  else (Accepts or 15-min expires - auto-accept)
  endif
else (Personal Worker - account holder performs work)
endif

:Worker checks liability ack checkbox\nand taps "Begin Work"\nJob status -> In Progress\nTimestamp recorded\nRequester notified;

:Proceed to UC-12 (Mark Complete)\nor UC-13 (Cannot Complete);

stop

@enduml

@startuml UC-12
' SnowReach - Use Case Diagrams - Group C: Work Execution and Completion

skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #f5f5f5
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #555555
skinparam ActivityDiamondBackgroundColor #fff3cd
skinparam ActivityDiamondBorderColor #856404
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #e8f4f8
skinparam NoteBorderColor #2980b9
skinparam ArrowColor #333333

title UC-12 - Complete Work (Mark Complete)

start

:Precondition: Job is In Progress.;

:Worker taps "Mark Complete";

:System prompts for completion photos\n(up to 5 - optional but encouraged);

if (Photos uploaded successfully?) then (yes)
  :Photos attached to job record;
elseif (Upload fails?) then (yes)
  :Non-blocking - job continues\nFlagged "No completion photos"\n(visible to Admin and Requester);
else (Worker skips photos)
  :No photos - job flagged\n(visible to Admin and Requester);
endif

:Worker taps "Confirm Completion";

:Job status -> Complete\n2-hr quality dispute window starts now.\n24-hr property damage window starts now.\nRating prompt queued to fire\n1 hour after terminal state is reached.\nRequester notified of both window times.;

:Proceed to UC-14 (Acknowledge)\nor UC-15 (Dispute);

stop

@enduml

@startuml UC-13
' SnowReach - Use Case Diagrams - Group C: Work Execution and Completion

skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #f5f5f5
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #555555
skinparam ActivityDiamondBackgroundColor #fff3cd
skinparam ActivityDiamondBorderColor #856404
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #e8f4f8
skinparam NoteBorderColor #2980b9
skinparam ArrowColor #333333

title UC-13 - Report Cannot Complete

start

:Precondition: Job is In Progress.\nWorker is unable to finish.;

:Worker taps "Cannot Complete";

:Mandatory reason selection\nOptions:\n- Equipment failure\n- Safety concern\n- Property access blocked\n- Weather conditions\n- Other;

:Worker selects reason and optionally\nenters explanatory note (max 500 chars);

:Worker taps "Submit" (irreversible once confirmed);

:Job status -> Incomplete\nWorker -> Available immediately\nBoth parties notified\nMessaging thread stays open\nWorker's Cannot Complete rate incremented.\nIf 3rd incident within 90 days:\nAdmin review flag auto-created.;

:Requester sees resolution screen\nwith 24-hour countdown;

if (Requester decision within 24 hours?) then (Accept Outcome)
  :Meaningful work acknowledged\nFunds released to Worker\n85% / 15% split\nJob -> Released;
  stop
elseif (Request Refund?) then (yes)
  :Full refund to Requester\nNo fault assigned to Worker\nJob -> Refunded;
  stop
elseif (Raise Dispute?) then (yes)
  :Dispute type pre-set: "Incomplete work"\nCannot Complete reason code and note\nincluded in evidence package\nProceed to UC-15;
  stop
else (No action - 24 hours expires)
  :Auto-refund fires\nFull refund to Requester\nJob -> Refunded;
  stop
endif

@enduml

@startuml UC-14
' SnowReach - Use Case Diagrams - Group C: Work Execution and Completion

skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #f5f5f5
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #555555
skinparam ActivityDiamondBackgroundColor #fff3cd
skinparam ActivityDiamondBorderColor #856404
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #e8f4f8
skinparam NoteBorderColor #2980b9
skinparam ArrowColor #333333

title UC-14 - Acknowledge Completion

start

:Precondition: Job is in Complete state.\n2-hr quality window and\n24-hr damage window are both active.;

:Requester receives completion notification\nand reviews job record and completion photos;

if (Requester action within 2-hr quality window?) then (Approve and Release)
  :Requester taps "Approve and Release"\nJob -> Released\nPhase 1: card charged\nPhase 2: escrow released\nWorker receives 85% within 2-3 business days\nRating prompt queued (fires 1hr later);
  stop
elseif (2-hr quality window expires - no dispute?) then (yes)
  :Auto-release fires\nSame disbursement as above\nJob -> Released;
  stop
else (Requester raises dispute within applicable window)
  :Proceed to UC-15 - Dispute;
  stop
endif

@enduml
